<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      i18n:domain="voteit.core">
<body>

<h3 i18n:translate="password_request_header">New password request from VoteIT</h3>

<div i18n:translate="password_request_body">
We've received a request to reset your password from VoteIT. Please follow the
link below to select a new password within 3 days. If you didn't request this yourself,
you don't have to do anything. Your old password will still work.
</div>

<div>
    <tal:trans i18n:translate="">Reset password link</tal:trans>:<br/>
    <a href="${pw_link}">${pw_link}</a>
</div>

<ul>
    <li><tal:trans i18n:translate="">UserID</tal:trans>: ${context.__name__}</li>
    <li><tal:trans i18n:translate="">Link to VoteIT</tal:trans>: ${request.application_url}</li>
</ul>

<div i18n:translate="">
Warm regards, The VoteIT team
</div>

</body>
</html>
